-- NLMK May Stop Financing La Louviere in December, Interfax Says
-- B y   S t e p a n   K r a v c h e n k o
-- 2012-11-28T19:16:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-28/nlmk-may-stop-financing-la-louviere-in-december-interfax-says.html
Novolipetsk Steel OJSC (NLMK) , Russian
billionaire  Vladimir Lisin ’s metals company, may stop financing
the Duferco La Louviere SA plant in Belgium this year, Interfax
reported, citing an unidentified person from the Russian
company.  This decision will be taken if the metal company fails to
reach an agreement with La Louviere’s workers on restructuring
the plant, Interfax said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stepan Kravchenko in Moscow at 
 skravchenko@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  